n Nortel increased its reserves for credit extended to customers by $767 mil=
lion in September, it effectively admitted it had booked sales in the past t=
o companies that couldn't pay--in effect overstating its performance in thos=
e earlier periods. In addition, Nortel says booking sales and accounting for=
