ry simple,'' says Moghadam. ``One company's numbers look better than another=
 one's even if they had identical fundamental results.''=20
There are other steps FASB could take to improve financial reporting and res=
tore GAAP's status. Trevor S. Harris, an accounting expert at Morgan Stanley=
